data.description: 5 bedrooms or 4 bedrooms with home office in the basement. Wrap around covered front porch! Oversized back deck - great for entertaining! Kitchen is updated and has granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and is open to the great room. Separate dining area. Nice size great room w/fireplace. Large owners bedroom with walk-in closet with custom built-ins. Owner's bath has a separate tub and shower, double vanity and updated cabinets. 3 additional bedrooms, full bath and laundry upstairs. Basement includes second living room or rec room, 5th bedroom or office/craft room and a large unfinished area for bathroom. Hardwood floors on the main. 2 car side entry garage with storage cabinets. Really nice lot with tons of play space and/or garden areas. Close to shopping, schools, Piedmont Hospital and the interstate. Community is part of Lakes of White Oak HOA which includes a pool, tennis courts and a park.
